content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:List of quests by release date

This is a list of quest release dates in reverse chronological order. The total possible quest points (QP) at the time of release of each quest is also given.

All quests released before Monkey Madness II are "vanilla" quests that were present in the August 2007 Archive of RuneScape at the time Old School RuneScape launched. Most quests released after were exclusively developed for Old School, but starting with Land of the Goblins some quests released in RuneScape after the August 2007 archive have been backported or extracted from the archive and re-released into Old School with some adjustments.
